          strange  stars  in  a  CFL  phase and develop a new pulsar kick
          mechanism  based  on  beaming  of  neutrino  emission along the
          magnetic   vortex  lines  and  parity  violation  of  the  weak
          interaction   neutrino-producing   Urca  process  in  a  strong
