          Title:  A  Detailed  Observation of a LMC Supernova Remnant DEM
          L241 with XMM-Newton
          Authors:  Aya Bamba (1), Masaru Ueno (2), Hiroshi Nakajima (3),
          Koji  Mori  (4), Katsuji Koyama (3) ((1) RIKEN, (2) Tokyo Inst.
