          comparison  with  results  from  numerical  simulations.  These
          results   provide   basic  statistical  information  about  the
          fluctuations   of   the  interactions  (i)  of  the  masses  in
          self-gravitating  systems like those encountered in the context
          of  cosmological N-body simulations, and (ii) of the charges in
