          We  have  investigated  the  proof  of the $H$ theorem within a
          manifestly  covariant  approach by considering the relativistic
          statistical  theory developed in [Phy. Rev. E {\bf 66}, 056125,
          2002;  {\it  ibid.}  {\bf  72},  036108 2005]. In our analysis,
          however,   we   have  not  considered  the  so-called  deformed
