          inflation  are  present in the flat directions of the Minimally
          Supersymmetric  Standard  Model. We show that out of many gauge
          invariant  combinations of squarks, sleptons and Higgses, there
          are  two  directions,  ${\bf  LLe}$, and ${\bf udd}$, which are
