          is  presented  which is essentially different from the one used
          in  the  pioneering  paper  by  Contopoulos,  Kazanas and Fendt
          (CKF).  The  problem  of  finding  the solutions was reduced to
          finding  expansion coefficients of the source term in a base of
          orthogonal  functions  on  the  unit  interval  by minimizing a
          multi-variable mismatch function defined on the light cylinder.
