          Ul'yanov   (IRA,  Kharkov),  A.A.  Deshpande  (RRI,  Bangalore;
          Arecibo),  A.A.  Ershov  (PRAO  Asc Lpi), V.V. Zakharenko (IRA,
          Kharkov),  V.I.  Kondratiev  (ASC Lpi), S.V. Kostyuk (ASC Lpi),
          B.Ya. Losovskii (PRAO Asc Lpi), V.A. Soglasnov (ASC Lpi)
          Comments:  13 pages, 1 figure, 1 table (originally published in
