          Title:  Neutrino chirality flip in a supernova and the bound on
          the neutrino magnetic moment
          Authors:  A.V.  Kuznetsov,  N.V. Mikheev (Yaroslavl State (P.G.
          Demidov) University, Russia)
          Comments:  7  pages,  LaTeX,  5  EPS figures, based on the talk
