          Title:  Resolved  Spectroscopy of M Dwarf/L Dwarf Binaries. II.
          2MASS J 17072343-0558249AB
          Authors: Michael W. McElwain, Adam J. Burgasser
          We  present  IRTF  SpeX  observations  of the M/L binary system
          2MASS  J17072343-0558249. SpeX imaging resolves the system into
          a  1"01+/-0.17  visual binary in which both components have red
          near  infrared  colors. Resolved low-resolution (R~150) 0.8-2.5
          micron  spectroscopy  reveals  strong H2O, CO and FeH bands and
          alkali  lines in the spectra of both components, characteristic
