          We study the dipolar magnetic field configuration in dependence
          on  brane tension and present solutions of Maxwell equations in
          the  internal and external background spacetime of a magnetized
          spherical  star  in  a  Randall-Sundrum II type braneworld. The
          star  is  modelled  as  sphere  consisting  of  perfect  highly
          magnetized  fluid  with  infinite  conductivity  and  frozen-in
