astro-ph/0609386 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Nucleonic gamma-ray production in Pulsar Wind Nebulae
          Authors: D. Horns (1), F. Aharonian (2), A.I.D. Hoffmann (1),
          A. Santangelo (1) ((1) IAAT, Univ. Tuebingen (2) Max-Planck
