astro-ph/0609535 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: The Nature of the Secondary Star in the Black Hole X-Ray
          Transient V616 Mon (=A0620-00)
          Authors: Thomas E. Harrison, Steve B. Howell, Paula Szkody,
