          data. The timing and spectral analysis was done using publicly
          available Swift, INTEGRAL, BeppoSAX, and RXTE/ASM data in the
          0.7-150 keV energy band. The source spectrum is described well
          by a highly absorbed (N_H~10^23 cm^-2) power law with a
