          G337.2+0.1 (=AX J1635.9-4719). The object shows centrally
          filled and diffuse X-ray emission. The emission peaks in the
          hard 3.0-10.0 keV band. A spatially resolved spectral study
          confirms that the column density of the central part of the SNR
          is about N_{H}~5.9 +/- 1.5*10^{22} cm^{-2} and its X-ray
