          photon index Gamma=0.96 +/- 0.56. The non-detection of line
          emission in the central spectrum is consistent with synchrotron
          radiation from a population of relativistic electrons. Detailed
          spectral analysis indicates that the outer region is highly
          absorbed and quite softer than the inner region, with
          N_{H}~16.2(+/-5.2)*10^{22} cm^{-2} and kT=4.4(+/-2.8) keV. Such
