          confirm the SNR nature of G337.2+0.1, and suggest that the
          central region of the source is a pulsar wind nebula (PWN),
          originated by an energetic though yet undetected pulsar, that
          is currently losing energy at a rate of ~ 10^{36} erg s^{-1}.


   
