          post-Newtonian (PN), and non-adiabatic resummed-PN models. From
          the ring-down portion of the GW we extract the fundamental
          quasi-normal mode and several of the overtones. Finally, we
          estimate the optimal signal-to-noise ratio for typical binaries
          detectable by GW experiments.


   
