          concentrated on timing analysis of the strong variability
          focusing on its aperiodic variability on short (<1s) time
          scales. In the power density spectra, we found a feature which
          is seen in many transient systems, but until now was not
          detected in GRS 1915+105 due to its elusiveness. As this
