          K_{abs}=54+/- 2 km s^-1. The orbital period of this system is
          found to be 0.4593249(1)d. The masses of the stars, their mass
          ratio and their separation are found to be M_1 sin^3 i =
          0.015+/-0.002 M_sun, M_2 sin^3 i = 0.007+/-0.002 M_sun, q =
