astro-ph/0611659 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Measuring Neutron Star Mass and Radius with Three
          Mass-Radius Relations
          Authors: C. M. Zhang, H.X. Yin, Y. Kojima, H. K. Chang, R. X.
          Xu, X. D. Li, B. Zhang, B. Kiziltan
          Comments: 8 pages, 3 figures, accepted by MNRAS
