          fitted with a broken power-law model with a break at
          1.57^{+0.21}_{-0.20}\times 10^{38} erg s^{-1}, while the
          profile of the disk population's XLF agrees with a single
          power-law distribution with a slope of 0.93^{+0.07}_{-0.06}.
