astro-ph/0701578 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Relativistic MHD Winds from Rotating Neutron Stars
          Authors: Bucciantini, N. (1), Thompson, Todd A. (2), Arons, J.
          (1), Quataert, E. (1), Del Zanna, L. (3) ((1) Astronomy Dep.,
