          significant gravitational recoil can also be obtained in these
          situations. We consider the case of black holes with opposite
          spins of magnitude $a$ aligned/anti-aligned with the orbital
          angular momentum, with $a$ the dimensionless spin parameters of
          the individual holes. For the initial setups under
          consideration, we find a recoil velocity of $V = 475 \KMS a$.
