          sources with luminosities higher than 8e33 erg/s in the 0.5--7
          keV band. The remaining (unresolved) emission closely follows
          the galaxy's optical light and is characterized by an
          emissivity per unit stellar mass of ~4.3e27 erg/s/M_sun in the
