          example, the gravitational wave background is dominated by a
          small number of distinct astrophysical sources. No signal was
          seen. Upper limit maps were produced assuming two different
          power laws for the source strain power spectrum. For an f^-3
          power law and using the 50 Hz to 1.8 kHz band the upper limits
