   [9]  @arXiv:0704.0133 [ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: PAH emission and star formation in the host of the
          z~2.56 Cloverleaf QSO
          Authors: D. Lutz, E. Sturm, L.J. Tacconi, E. Valiante, M.
          Schweitzer, H. Netzer, R. Maiolino, P. Andreani, O. Shemmer, S.
