          We report the first detection of the 6.2micron and 7.7micron
          infrared `PAH' emission features in the spectrum of a high
          redshift QSO, from the Spitzer-IRS spectrum of the Cloverleaf
          lensed QSO (H1413+117, z~2.56). The ratio of PAH features and
