   [23]  @arXiv:0704.0209 [ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Chandra Observations of Supernova 1987A
          Authors: Sangwook Park, David N. Burrows, Gordon P. Garmire
          (Penn State), Richard McCray (Colorado), Judith L. Racusin
          (Penn State), Svetozar A. Zhekov (Space Res Inst)
          Comments: 8 pages, 4 figures (including 2 color figs), 3
