   [1]  @arXiv:0704.0253 [ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: The Spitzer c2d Survey of Large, Nearby, Interstellar
          Clouds VIII. Serpens Observed with MIPS
          Authors: Paul M. Harvey, Luisa M. Rebull, Tim Brooke, William
          J. Spiesman, Nicholas Chapman, Tracy L. Huard, Neal J. Evans
          II, Lucas Cieza, Shih-Ping Lai, Lori E. Allen, Lee G. Mundy,
