   [23]  @arXiv:0704.0316 [ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: The Millennium Galaxy Catalogue: The local supermassive
          black hole mass function in early- and late-type galaxies
          Authors: Alister W. Graham, Simon P. Driver, Paul D. Allen,
          Jochen Liske
          Comments: 10 pages of text plus 5 of figs and refs. MNRAS,
