          cosmic-ray electrons with the solar radiation. The emission was
          predicted to contribute to the diffuse extragalactic background
          even at large angular distances from the Sun. While this
          emission is expected to be readily detectable in future by
          GLAST, the situation for available EGRET data is more
          challenging. We present a detailed study of the EGRET database,
